        public AHJPlusPSAPResponse getAHJPlusPSAPByAddress(String address)
                                            throws ApiException
        AHJ & PSAP By Address. Accepts addresses as input and Returns contact details for Authorities Having Jurisdiction (AHJ) on-behalf-of local Public Safety Answering Points (PSAP). 911/PSAP accepts an address and returns PSAP contact data plus contact data for an AHJ to communicate directly with a PSAP. Details include agency name, phone number, city name, coverage, contact person's details, site details and mailing addresses for EMS, Fire, and Police PSAP contacts.
